Scrapyard - Bomb Defusal by Sadist
Description: Terrorists have been hiding their bomb making parts in the local scrapyard.  The SAS have received a evidence of terrorist plots, and have been sent to investigate.
Terrorist Objective: Destroy the evidence using C4 explosives.  
Counter-Terrorist Objective: Stop the terrorists from shipping the bomb parts, and foil the terrorist plot.
